        <p>I also make fanmade charts for <a href=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vnKOcJwmyVM>Arcaea</a>, <a href=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BG_wPji-hkc>Dynamix</a>, and <a href=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_vcooCMrdBo>maimai DX</a>.</p>
